    "rich_text_yc7baL": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "subheading_m3JDM8": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "MUMU BATH WHERE OLIVE OIL MEETS LUXURY"
          }
        },
        "heading_x7BnnX": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Nature's Secret for Radiant Skin is found with Olive Oil Soaps",
            "heading_tag": "h2"
          }
        },
        "richtext_4yphFz": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Gentle, pure, and deeply moisturizing - our soaps are<br/>crafted to care for even the most sensitive skin. Rich in vitamins and<br/>antioxidants, they cleanse without stripping your skin’s natural moisture.</p><p>Made in small batches with high-quality plant-based<br/>ingredients, each bar is a celebration of simple, clean skincare. Discover the<br/>timeless benefits of olive oil and give your skin the love it deserves.</p><h2>Why Choose Olive Oil Soap?</h2><p><strong>Deep Moisturization</strong>: Olive oil closely mimics your skin's natural lipids, penetrating deeply to combat dehydration.</p><p><strong>Gentle Cleansing</strong>: Our soaps cleanse without stripping, leaving your skin soft and supple.</p><p><strong>Rich in Antioxidants</strong>: Olive oil helps fight free radicals, promoting healthier and younger-looking skin.</p><p><strong>Suitable for All Skin Types</strong>: From dry and mature to combination and oily, our soaps cater to every skin need.</p><p><strong>Ancient Wisdom, Modern Care</strong>: Used by ancient civilizations, olive oil continues to be a skincare powerhouse.</p><h2>Olive Oil Soap Collection by Mumu Bath</h2><p>Explore our range of handcrafted <strong>olive<br/>oil soap bars</strong>, each designed to address<br/>specific skin concerns:</p><p><a href=\"/products/eczema-soap\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Morning Dew Eczema Relief Soap\"><strong>Morning Dew Eczema Relief Soap</strong></a>: Soothe irritated skin and find relief from eczema.</p><p><a href=\"/products/kiss-me-sunshine\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Kiss Me Sunshine Soap Bar\"><strong>Kiss Me Sunshine Soap Bar</strong></a>: Brighten your day and your skin with this uplifting blend.</p><p><a href=\"/products/walk-in-the-woods-mens-bar\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Walk in The Woods Soap Bar\"><strong>Walk in The Woods Soap Bar</strong></a>: Experience nature's freshness with every wash.</p><p><a href=\"/products/lavender-oasis\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lavender Oasis Organic Soap\"><strong>Lavender Oasis Organic Soap</strong></a>: Relax and rejuvenate with the calming scent of lavender.</p><p><a href=\"/products/all-in-one-body-shampoo-bar\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"All-In-One Body & Shampoo Bar\"><strong>All-In-One Body & Shampoo Bar</strong></a>: Simplify your routine with this multi-tasking marvel.</p><p><a href=\"/products/super-simple-baby-bar\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Super Simple Baby Bar Soap\"><strong>Super Simple Baby Bar Soap</strong></a>: Gentle enough for the most delicate skin.</p><p><a href=\"/products/signature-hydrating-facial\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Signature Hydrating Facial Soap Bar\"><strong>Signature Hydrating Facial Soap Bar</strong></a>: Give your face the nourishment it deserves.</p><p><a href=\"/products/french-clay-facial-soap\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"French Clay Facial Soap\"><strong>French Clay Facial Soap</strong></a>: Detoxify and clarify with the power of French clay.</p><p></p><h2>How to Use for Best Results</h2><p>Enjoy the full benefits of our nourishing olive oil soap<br/>with just a few mindful steps. Gentle, effective, and ideal for daily use.</p><p><strong>Lather Gently with Warm Water</strong> – Wet your hands and create a rich lather before <a>applying</a> to your skin. This activates the natural oils<br/>and prepares the soap for cleansing.</p><p><strong>Massage onto Damp Skin</strong> – Apply to face and body in circular motions. For <strong>olive oil soap for </strong><a><strong>face</strong></a><strong>,</strong> be especially gentle to avoid over-cleansing.</p><p><strong>Rinse Thoroughly</strong> – Use lukewarm water to wash away the lather completely.<br/>Pat skin dry to lock in moisture.</p><p><strong>Follow with Rejuvenating Face Cream</strong> – After cleansing, apply our Rejuvenating Face Cream to nourish and hydrate. This seals in the softness <a>from </a>the soap.</p><p><strong>Store on a Draining Soap Dish</strong> – Keep your bar dry between uses. This helps extend the life of your handcrafted soap naturally.</p><h2>The Mumu Bath Difference</h2><p>At Mumu Bath, we craft our <strong>olive soaps</strong> with a base of olive and coconut oils. Our commitment to quality ensures that each bar is:</p><ul><li>Organic</li><li>Biodegradable</li><li>Cruelty-free</li><li>Made in the USA</li></ul><h2>Your Skin Deserves the Pure Power of Olive Oil</h2><p>Experience the transformative power of olive oil soap <strong>bars</strong>. Your skin will thank you for choosing Mumu Bath's natural, nourishing, and eco-friendly products.</p><p>Shop our Olive Oil Soap collection now and unveil your skin's natural radiance!</p>"
          }
        }
      },
